        <a target="_blank" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/rodolfo-bernardes-38653b19a/">Rodolfo</a>,
        <a target="_blank" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/sergisleymatias/">Sergisley</a> e
        <a target="_blank" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/darife/">Daniel</a></p>
    </div>
  </footer>

